{MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 100 "15.  Pi is the nume
rical quantity and pi is the greek letter.  The following sequence exp
loits this." }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 6 "pi=Pi;" }}}
{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 9 "evalf(%);" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 
"> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 10 "evalf(pi);" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
